title Play Order Test

function notify audio msg
    text <msg>
    play <audio>
endfunction

function notify_sound_first audio msg
    play <audio>
    text <msg>
endfunction

text Test 1: Text before sound. Dialog shows first, sound plays after dismissing.
call notify achievement1.ogg "Text came first!"

wait 500

text Test 2: Sound before text. Sound and dialog overlap.
call notify_sound_first achievement1.ogg "Sound came first!"

text Done.
end
